# 06/02/2015
# Written by: SPS

# This repository has the source code of a program to display ascii text file.
# This C program is written for a GNU/Linux system.
# Dependency : "ncurses" C library

Steps to download the source code and compile it
------------------------------------------------
1. Make a local copy of the source code:

	$ cd ~
	$ git clone https://github.com/1sps/ed8.git

2. Compile the source code:

	$ cd ~/ed8
	$ make

Steps to run the program
------------------------
1. To run:

	$ cd ~/ed8
	$ ./ed8

Steps to uninstall the program 
------------------------------
1. To uninstall

	$ cd ~/ed8
	$ make clean

